                                                                                                                                Indicators and status

                                                                                                                                Tag

                                                                                                                                A tag is a static and actionable component that displays an element's status, key properties, or categories, and allows users to input information for filtering content.

                                                                                                                                Usage
                                                                                                                                Content
                                                                                                                                Spec
                                                                                                                                Status & changelog

                                                                                                                                Type and Color

                                                                                                                                Text styles

                                                                                                                                Every tag uses Label style with their respective sizes.

                                                                                                                                Large
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Text: LabelLarge

                                                                                                                                Medium
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Text: LabelMedium

                                                                                                                                Small
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Text: LabelSmall

                                                                                                                                Extra small
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Text: LabelXSmall

                                                                                                                                Dark mode

                                                                                                                                Tags have custom colors assigned to them but need to work in dark mode. If you use Base’s tags out of the box, you won’t have to worry about dark mode. The color tokens will convert to work properly in dark mode.

                                                                                                                                Color tokens

                                                                                                                                All Tags use primitive color tokens because Tag colors are not assigned to specific semantics. Below shows standard colors but Tags can be customized to the user's needs.

                                                                                                                                Screen readers

                                                                                                                                VoiceOver

                                                                                                                                In most cases, tags are used to display metadata which in VoiceOver should be considered part of the content and should be read alongside labels. Actionable tags are considered as buttons.

                                                                                                                                Add notes
